    "data": [
        {
            "id": 6364764,
            "title": "〈焦點股〉大反攻滿堂紅 光通訊股卻黯淡無光 光聖失守2000元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (5) 日在美股四大指數齊揚下，電子權值股回神，指數一度強彈近 1500 點，盤中雖漲幅收斂，但仍上漲近 800 點，但盤面上光通訊概念股則是受漲多賣壓影響，多檔開高走低，包括龍頭股光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>) 盤中下跌超過百點，跌逾半根停板，失守 2,000 元大關，包括東典光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6588:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6588\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6588-TW</a>)、華星光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)、統新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6426:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6426\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6426-TW</a>) 更一度亮燈跌停，整體族群類股於盤中豬羊變色、多檔慘綠。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6364764/l/5533da607fc350e7e0b3f2803125f5fe.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">矽光子概念股大反攻日失利，光通訊族群股多檔慘綠。 (圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今日在亞洲強勁反彈下，重返月線大關，早盤一舉改寫歷史次高漲點紀錄，包括台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 更大漲 8%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 等權值股吹起反攻號角領大盤往前衝。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光通訊股近期則受惠於矽光子 (CPO) 需求強勁，加上輝達與光學元件製造商 Coherent 達成策略協議下共推光學技術創新及產能擴張，台廠光通訊供應鏈近期也迎接一波漲勢，光聖更一度登上 2500 元大關，創新天價。。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>但隨本周大盤歷經美伊戰事衝擊，近期漲高的光通訊族群紛紛中箭落馬，今日除了光聖、東典光電、華星光、統新重挫，包括波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>) 盤中最低也跌到 650 元，跌點超過 100 元，聯鈞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3450:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3450\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3450-TW</a>)、光環 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3234:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3234\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3234-TW</a>)、聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)，盤中後也一度下跌超過半根停板，尾盤跌幅才逐漸收斂。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>分析師表示，光通訊因為近期漲勢凌厲，多檔股價走勢與季線乖離率大，在反攻日當下，容易形成法人要抽回資金的對象，股價難免遭到獲利賣壓導致下修，投資人不用急著進場追低，可待整體回跌盤勢穩定後，持續觀察獲利及營收表現，再逢低承接。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6364764",
